Revision history for Badge-Depot-Plugin-Kwalitee

0.0103 2016-08-12 17:54:02 UTC
 [Enhancements]
 - Relaxes 'author' attribute. It is no longer required to create the badge
   object, but if author is missing the kwalitee will be 'unknown'. This
   change makes releases that uses this badge but was done before v0.0102
   rebuildable.

 [Stats & Dependency Changes]
 - 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
 - (dev sug) ~ Dist::Iller::Config::Author::CSSON 0.0311 --> 0.0312

0.0102 2016-08-11T23:55:28Z UTC
 [Other Changes]
 - Default url protocol (temporarily) changed from https to http.

 [Bug Fixes]
 - Added required 'author' attribute in order to adapt to cpants changes.

 [Stats & Dependency Changes]
 - 2 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)
 - (dev req) + Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MetaConfig (any)
 - (dev req) + Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PromptIfStale (any)
 - (dev sug) ~ Dist::Iller 0.1407 --> 0.1408
 - (dev sug) ~ Dist::Iller::Config::Author::CSSON 0.0309 --> 0.0311

0.0101 2016-02-22T14:40:15Z UTC
 [Enhancements]
 - Now uses the Dist::Zilla object (if it is used during a Dist::Zilla
   build) to set the 'dist' and 'version' attributes.

 [Documentation]
 - Fix abstract.

